text:
MY NEW YEAR'S RESOLUTIONS

Be more judgmental
Lose twenty galaxies 
Exorcise more
Think before I smite
Spend more time with Junior
Floss!

Tonight Dick Clark will rock heaven into 2014 with live performances by Hendrix, Joplin and Lennon!
(No MJ, though. He doesn't live here.)
Wishing everyone a happy 2015. That's not a typo. I know what's coming next year and no waaaaay is it going to make you happy.
The Second Amendment grants every American the right to compensate for his tiny, tiny penis.
The things people believe in are unbelievable.
One-third of Americans don't believe in evolution. Or, evidently, evolving.
Shit, did I miss Jesus's birthday?
I would have no problem with suicide bombers if they limited it to suicide.
Yep. I hate Jerry Jones.
With great power comes zero accountability.
It's the last Saturday night of the year. Getteth thee some.
Happy birthday Stan Lee, from one creation mythologist to another.
I have absolutely no plan for your life.
I say this every New Year and I never follow through because I get distracted or lazy but I swear, 2014 WILL be the year I kill you all.
Anyone who retweets this is an asshole.
Homophobia is a sacred union between a man and a bible.
Jesus is loving his PrayStation 4! So far his favorite games are "Call of Duty: Holy Ghosts" and, more surprisingly, "Killzone". #greatkid
Merry Christmas, douchebags.
Justin Bieber's career died for your sins.
WARNING: U.S. radar has detected a mysterious bearded figure bombarding innocent children in the name of religion. #al-Kinda

"Knock knock."
"Who's there?"
"Mary and Joseph."
"No vacancy."
An old white man in a beard bestowing gifts from the sky? Please.
Spelling errors make baby Jesus crie.
Toronto, do I even have to TELL you what I'm punishing you for?
The problem with rich people is you're not one of them.
Traditional marriage was between a boy's parents and a girl's parents. And maybe some cattle.
All I want for Christmas is you. #ALotScarierWhenISayIt
If you retweet Me 20 times you get to kill a guy.
This year for his birthday Jesus wants an Xbox. Not the console; a box for his cross.
I am not a parody account. I am The Lord thy God, King of the Universe, and I am communicating by Twitter because My fax is broken.
The true meaning of Christmas is buying shit.
On the sixth day I created mankind and I've been doing damage control ever since.
Tweeting something stupid is like thinking something stupid only much, much more stupid.
Nature made ducks sound like ducks and people sound like people. To act differently is to go against nature.
If you start allowing gay people to get married, then whats next? Gay people being happy?!? #slipperyslope
You have a constitutionally-protected right to verbally express your complete misunderstanding of your constitutionally-protected rights.
I created Adam and Eve, not Adam and some stupid asshole making artificial duck sounds.
Never confuse a stroke of good fortune with Me caring about you.
People who are "born again" were born two too many times.
It's always the people who believe I exist who provide the strongest evidence I don't.
I genuinely don't remember making you all this stupid.
Dont mess with Texas. Cause its easily confused.
Hating people is a lifestyle choice.
I created straight people to give gay people someone to dress better than.
The Duck Dynasty guy who likened homosexuality to bestiality makes a living helping people trick ducks into thinking they want to fuck them.
Instagramming daily selfies does not constitute personal growth.
Over 80% of the universe is composed of stupid.
If it's any consolation, when I pray to Myself I don't get an answer either.
Stop and ask yourself, "What would I do with my life if I didn't need the money?" Then, resume the miserable job you do for money.
Wait till you guys find out the Mayans were only off by a year.
It was right around the time I sent My only son to die on the cross that I realized there was something seriously wrong with Me.
What do Me, Santa Claus and the Easter Bunny have in common? You guessed it: we're all white.
Many of you suck.
SPOILER ALERT: Worms eat you.
It is unusually cold in a particular place today. Therefore global warming is a hoax.
There is snow on the pyramids of Egypt for the first time in 112 years. It begins. #seeyousoon
Keep the Bible out of the uterus. It's cramped enough in there already.
Christmas is a very awkward time of year for people who are Jewish. Jesus, for example.
Jesus owned several guns. He used them for hunting and self-defense. He resisted all attempts by the Roman empire to confiscate his guns.
Jesus was white and spoke English and enjoyed baseball and apple pie and was a churchgoing Christian.
People keep asking Me why I created mosquitoes. To bite you repeatedly and give you malaria, that's why.
I thought it would be fun to make most of you stupid, but it turns out it's more annoying than amusing.
I know you doubt Me, I know you have anger towards Me, I know you question the goodness of My intentions, but come on: give it up for boobs.
It's hard to book a party for My son's birthday because it happens to fall on Christmas.
Sometimes it can be hard to stay positive, what with everything sucking and all.
Never, ever retweet this.
The best way to honor Nelson Mandela's memory is, in whatever way is most appropriate and relevant for you, to quit being such an asshole.
Being human is hard. I feel bad for you guys. Not bad enough, obviously, but bad.
I sure seem to have a thing for Auburn this year, huh?
Saturday night is for moaning My name. Sunday morning is for chanting it.
The best way to believe every word of the Bible is not to read it.
I don't have an anger problem. I get angry. I smite people. I feel better. No problem.
When you wish upon a star, makes no difference who you are. It ain't gonna work.
Jesus and Mandela are hitting it off splendidly. I knew they would. They're both huge rugby fans.
RIP Nelson Mandela.
Jesus died for your sins, so make 'em count. Like, screw a horse or something.
People who brag about being politically incorrect tend to also be morally, ethically, factually, and grammatically incorrect.
#stupidity is trending. Not on Twitter, just in general.
I'm thinking about writing the Bible again, only this time not on meth.
I see you when you're sleeping. I know when you're awake. I know if you've been bad or good, and your soul is doomed to bake.
I'm making My list. I'm checking it twice. Your souls are all full of unspeakable vice. Most of you are going to hell.
You better watch out. You better not cry. You better not pout. I'm telling you why. Most of you are going to hell.
I shot the seraph. But I didn't shoot the cherubim.
